City of David United Football Club, nke a maara nke ọma dị ka COD United bụ klọb bọọlụ ọkachamara nke Naijiria nke dị na Lagos State, Naijiria
Ha na-egwu na National League nke Naịjirịa, ọkwa nke abụọ kachasị elu nke bọọlụ ọkachamara na Naịjirị
E guzobere klọb ahụ na 2007 site na parish City of David nke Redeemed Christian Church of God, ma na-egwu egwuregwu ụlọ ya na Onikan Stadium.
N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2013, ndị otu ahụ meriri Lagos State FA Cup, site na imeri MFM FC ma nọchite anya steeti ahụ na ọkwa mba
O nwekwara nkwekọrịta mmekọrịta na Bolton Wanderers na Bournemouth nke England.
COD United F.C nwere otu bọọlụ asaa nke gụnyere U-10, U-12, U-14, U-16 na U-21 otu
Onye isi nchịkwa na-achịkwa nke ọ bụla n'ime ndị otu ndị a, ebe onye nduzi teknụzụ na-elekọta usoro bọọlụ COD United dum.
C.O.D United FC bụ nke City of David parish nke Redeemed Christian Church of God guzobere na Septemba 2007
Ha malitere ịsọ mpi na Amateur Division III ma n'oge na-adịghị anya nweta nkwalite iji gbaa bọọlụ na Amateur division II na 2009
Ka ọ na-erule n'afọ 2011, COD United gbara bọọlụ na Amateur Division I, nke a sochiri nke mbụ ya na Nigerian National Division 1 n'afọ 2012
Klọb ahụ na nnukwu iko mbụ ya na 2013 site na mmeri Lagos State FA Cup, na-emeri MFM FC nke Lagos
Klọb ahụ na Maachị 2016 họpụtara onye nkuzi a ma ama, Festus Allen dị ka onye njikwa nke ndị otu okenye.
